![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578251347295-3AYVSV458XOF87S17I9T/image-asset.jpeg?format=original)

Happy Belated Cliquemas all! What a year it has been, filled to the brim with latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media! We laughed, we cried, and ultimately we became better Cliquers! So with all the dust settled and a new chapter in front of us, consider this week’s episode the “post credit” for 2018, as we put on our thinking caps and look to the future to try and predict the comings and goings on 2019!

What will be the box office hit of the year? What comic book character will soar in popularity? What new shows will set the standard for what it means to be a comic book show? 2019 comes one week early on Major Issues!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

